Unfortunately, the guarantees on the quantile don't work by value, but by element count.  The approximate median returned is the element that is in position +/- eps*data.size() of the true median.  Thus to get the upper and lower bounds, you need to actually do: 
```
const double upper_bound = sketch->get_quantile(0.5 + epsilon * data.size()); 
const double lower_bound = sketch->get_quantile(0.5 - epsilon * data.size()); 
```

